'''Corellia StarDrive''' was a successful, if short-lived, [[Starship/Legends|starship]] manufacturer. The company was founded by a former [[Corellian Engineering Corporation/Legends|Corellian Engineering Corporation]] executive one [[Millennium/Legends|millennia]] before the outbreak of the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]]. Corellia StarDrive was well known for both its civilian and military vehicles; many warships of the [[Republic Navy/Legends|Republic Navy]] were constructed by Corellia StarDrive much to the concertation of Corellian Engineering Corporation.<ref name="EGVV" />

Corellia StarDrive was the parent company of [[Akin-Dower]]. During the [[Galactic War]], the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]] invaded [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. In this time, Corellia StarDrive used its corporate finances to fund the rebellion against the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]]. As a result, the Empire destroyed their headquarters in order to deal a crippling blow on the company.

Corellia StarDrive's supremacy did not last long; the whole of the company's senior design team was killed in a freak [[Shuttle/Legends|shuttle]] crash. Corellia StarDrive never fully recovered from the loss and was subsequently bought by Corellian Engineering Corporation around two millennia after it was formed.<ref name="EGVV" />

